body:
It is extremely unfair having an afk in your game. Especially when your winning lane then get rekt because someone decides to AFK. We should lose less LP when we have an AFK and make players who AFK lose more LP. 

If someone has left the game for more than 5 minutes (there can be connection losses) then they lose % extra LP for a loss, or a win.
Additionally people lose a % less for having an afk for 5 minutes.

&quot;&quot; 10 minutes&quot;&quot;
&quot;&quot;15 minutes&quot;&quot;
&quot;&quot;20 minutes+&quot;&quot;

...

Lose % less LP for having 1 , 2 , 3 ,4  afks.

Making it so if someone has 4 AFKS for 20 minutes they lose 50% less LP.
